HEADWORD: Lycopsida
<hw>Lycopsida</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The class including club mosses
and related forms: includes Lycopodiales; Isoetales; Selaginellales; and
extinct Lepidodendrales; sometimes considered a subdivision of
Tracheophyta.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> class Lycopsida, Lycopodiate, class
Lycopodiate.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lycopus</ent>⟦br⟧
